# Apa itu CSS?

CSS (Cascading Style Sheets) digunakan untuk styling dan layout halaman web.

## Cara Menambahkan CSS

### 1. Inline CSS
```html
<p style="color: blue; font-size: 16px;">Teks biru</p>
```

### 2. Internal CSS
```html
<style>
    p {
        color: red;
        font-size: 18px;
    }
</style>
```

### 3. External CSS
```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
```

## Selector Dasar

```css
/* Selector elemen */
p {
    color: blue;
}

/* Selector class */
.text-red {
    color: red;
}

/* Selector ID */
#header {
    background: gray;
}
```

## Contoh Lengkap:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .judul {
            color: darkblue;
            text-align: center;
        }

        #container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="container">
        <h1 class="judul">Belajar CSS</h1>
        <p style="color: green;">Teks hijau dengan inline CSS</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

2.theory:
# Warna dan Background

## Sistem Warna CSS

### 1. Named Colors
```css
p {
    color: red;
    background-color: yellow;
}
```

### 2. HEX Colors
```css
h1 {
    color: #ff0000;        /* Merah */
    background: #00ff00;   /* Hijau */
}
```

### 3. RGB Colors
```css
div {
    color: rgb(255, 0, 0);     /* Merah */
    background: rgb(0, 255, 0); /* Hijau */
}
```

### 4. RGBA Colors (dengan opacity)
```css
.box {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.5); /* Biru 50% transparan */
}
```

## Background Properties

```css
.element {
    background-color: #f0f0f0;
    background-image: url('gambar.jpg');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: cover;
}
```

## Contoh Lengkap:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .highlight {
            background-color: #ffff00;
            color: #333;
            padding: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Website Saya</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <p>Ini adalah <span class="highlight">teks penting</span> yang perlu diperhatikan.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

3.theory:
# Styling Teks dan Font

## Text Properties

```css
p {
    color: #333;                    /* Warna teks */
    text-align: center;             /* Rata: left, center, right, justify */
    text-decoration: underline;     /* Dekorasi: underline, overline, line-through */
    text-transform: uppercase;      /* Transformasi: uppercase, lowercase, capitalize */
    line-height: 1.6;               /* Tinggi baris */
    letter-spacing: 1px;            /* Jarak antar huruf */
    word-spacing: 2px;              /* Jarak antar kata */
}
```

## Font Properties

```css
h1 {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;  /* Jenis font */
    font-size: 24px;                 /* Ukuran font */
    font-weight: bold;               /* Ketebalan: normal, bold, 100-900 */
    font-style: italic;              /* Gaya: normal, italic, oblique */
}
```

## Google Fonts

```html
<!-- Tambahkan di head -->
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<!-- Gunakan di CSS -->
<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    }

    .bold-text {
        font-weight: 700;
    }
</style>
```

## Contoh Lengkap:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .judul {
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .quote {
            font-style: italic;
            text-align: center;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        }

        .important {
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1 class="judul">Belajar CSS Typography</h1>

    <p class="quote">
        "Design is not just what it looks like and feels like. Design is how it works."
    </p>

    <p>
        Ini adalah teks biasa dengan <span class="important">bagian penting</span> 
        yang ditandai dengan tebal dan garis bawah.
    </p>
</body>
</html>
```

4.theory:
# CSS Box Model

Setiap elemen HTML adalah sebuah 'box' dengan properti:

## Komponen Box Model

```css
.box {
    width: 300px;           /* Lebar konten */
    height: 200px;          /* Tinggi konten */
    padding: 20px;          /* Jarak dalam */
    border: 2px solid #333; /* Border */
    margin: 10px;           /* Jarak luar */
}
```

## Margin dan Padding

```css
/* Semua sisi sama */
.element1 {
    margin: 10px;
    padding: 15px;
}

/* Vertikal & Horizontal */
.element2 {
    margin: 10px 20px;      /* top/bottom: 10px, left/right: 20px */
    padding: 5px 10px;
}

/* Individual sides */
.element3 {
    margin-top: 5px;
    margin-right: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    margin-left: 20px;

    /* Shorthand */
    padding: 5px 10px 15px 20px; /* top, right, bottom, left */
}
```

## Border Properties

```css
.border-example {
    border-width: 2px;
    border-style: solid;    /* solid, dotted, dashed, double */
    border-color: red;

    /* Shorthand */
    border: 2px solid red;

    /* Individual sides */
    border-top: 1px dotted blue;
    border-radius: 10px;    /* Sudut melengkung */
}
```

## Contoh Lengkap:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-left: 4px solid #fdcb6e;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .button {
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Card Title</h2>
            <p>Ini adalah konten card dengan padding dan margin.</p>
            <button class="button">Click Me</button>
        </div>

        <div class="highlight-box">
            Ini adalah box highlight dengan border kiri yang menonjol.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

5.theory:
# Display Property untuk Layout

## Display Values

### 1. Block
Elemen mengambil seluruh lebar parent.
```css
.block-element {
    display: block;      /* Default: div, p, h1-h6 */
    width: 100%;
}
```

### 2. Inline
Elemen hanya mengambil space yang dibutuhkan.
```css
.inline-element {
    display: inline;     /* Default: span, a, strong */
    /* width dan height tidak bekerja */
}
```

### 3. Inline-block
Gabungan inline dan block.
```css
.inline-block-element {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 100px;
    height: 50px;
}
```

### 4. None
Menyembunyikan elemen.
```css
.hidden {
    display: none;
}
```

## Contoh Layout:

```css
/* Navigation bar */
.nav {
    background: #333;
    padding: 10px;
}

.nav-item {
    display: inline-block;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.nav-item:hover {
    background: #555;
}

/* Card grid */
.card-container {
    text-align: center;
}

.card {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 200px;
    margin: 10px;
    padding: 15px;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 5px;
}
```

## Contoh Lengkap:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .navbar {
            background: #2c3e50;
            padding: 15px 0;
        }

        .nav-container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .nav-item {
            display: inline-block;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 0 5px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .nav-item:hover {
            background: #34495e;
        }

        .product-grid {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .product {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 200px;
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .hidden {
            display: none;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline;
            background: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="#" class="nav-item">Home</a>
            <a href="#" class="nav-item">Products</a>
            <a href="#" class="nav-item">About</a>
            <a href="#" class="nav-item">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="product-grid">
        <div class="product">
            <h3>Product 1 <span class="badge">New</span></h3>
            <p>Description here</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product">
            <h3>Product 2</h3>
            <p>Description here</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product hidden">
            <h3>Hidden Product</h3>
            <p>This is hidden</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

6.theory:
# CSS Positioning

## Position Values

### 1. Static (Default)
```css
.element {
    position: static;
}
```

### 2. Relative
```css
.element {
    position: relative;
    top: 10px;
    left: 20px;
}
```

### 3. Absolute
```css
.element {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
}
```

### 4. Fixed
```css
.element {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 20px;
    right: 20px;
}
```

### 5. Sticky
```css
.element {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
}
```

## Z-index
Mengontrol tumpukan elemen.

```css
.box1 {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}

.box2 {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2; /* Akan di atas box1 */
}
```

## Contoh Lengkap:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container {
            position: relative;
            height: 400px;
            border: 2px solid #333;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        .box {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            position: absolute;
        }

        .red {
            background: red;
            top: 50px;
            left: 50px;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .blue {
            background: blue;
            top: 80px;
            left: 80px;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .green {
            background: green;
            top: 110px;
            left: 110px;
            z-index: 3;
        }

        .fixed-button {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .sticky-header {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            z-index: 100;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="sticky-header">Sticky Header</div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="box red">Red (z:1)</div>
        <div class="box blue">Blue (z:2)</div>
        <div class="box green">Green (z:3)</div>
    </div>

    <button class="fixed-button">Fixed Button</button>
</body>
</html>
```
